{"word":"Jehoahaz","slug":"jehoahaz","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jehoahaz</b> <a href=\"#/H3059\">H3059</a><br/><a href=\"#/H3099\">H3099</a> <br/> 1. Son of Jehu, and king of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=35'>2Ki 10:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=13&verse=9'>2Ki 13:9</a><br/> 2. Son of Jehoram, king of Judah<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=17'>2Ch 21:17</a><br/><a href='S:Ahaziah'>Ahaziah</a> <br/> 3. Called Shallum<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=31'>2Ki 23:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=15'>1Ch 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=1'>2Ch 36:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=11'>Jer 22:11</a><br/> Wicked reign of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=32'>2Ki 23:32</a><br/> Pharaoh Nechoh, king of Egypt, invades the kingdom of, defeats him, and takes him captive to Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=35'>2Ki 23:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=4'>2Ch 36:4</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=12'>Jer 22:12</a>"}]}